Package wordEater

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Analyzer
    This class reads string (with addString() ), split the string in words, and either: - increment the occurrence of the word if it is already known - adds the word with an occurrence of 1 to its ordered list.
    wordEaterMain
    This little program reads a text and generates on the system console a report showing the occurrence of each word in the text, primarily sorted by word length, and secondary sorted by ASCII value of the word.
    WordOccurrence
    This class is stores a word and its associated number of occurrence.
